# ── Error IRQ scaffold ────────────────────────────────────────────────────────
# Tier 1 (QEMU-reachable): init with enable_interrupts=true, spurious-fire
# guard (handle_dma_irq with no bits set → ControllerNotReady), and
# assert state remains Ready after spurious fire.
#
# Tier 2 (hardware-only, marked TODO in source): write-protect (bit 9),
# DMA-abort (bit 10 in-flight), command-abort (bit 10 idle), DMA-complete
# (bit 11).  FMC IRQ number: 39 (ast1060_pac::Interrupt::fmc).
